  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The database will go live just before the IMF/WB annual meetings, to create maximum opportunity for advocacy impact.  The database, and the accompanying report (for which funding is being sought from RALF) will act as a pilot, to demonstrate the utility of the data and the analysis to global advocacy. It will be used to raise institutional funds by the end of 2012, for a more substantial work programme over 2013 -17.</narrative>
